---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { getLangFromUrl, useTranslations } from '../../i18n/utils';

const lang = getLangFromUrl(Astro.url);
const t = useTranslations(lang);
---

<BaseLayout title={`Privacy Policy - ${t('site.title')}`} lang={lang}>
  <div class="max-w-5xl w-full mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-36">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 md:mb-20">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-text tracking-tight mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-sub">Effective Date: January 1, 2025</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none
      prose-headings:font-semibold prose-headings:tracking-tight
      prose-h2:text-xl prose-h2:mt-12 prose-h2:mb-4
      prose-p:text-text-sub prose-p:leading-7
      prose-strong:text-text prose-strong:font-medium
    ">
      <h2>1. Purpose of Processing Personal Information</h2>
      <p>
        Hyewon & Insong ("Company") processes personal information for the following purposes.
        The personal information collected will not be used for any purpose other than those stated below.
        If the purpose of use changes, necessary measures such as obtaining separate consent will be taken.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Providing and operating app services</li>
        <li>Analyzing app errors and improving service stability</li>
        <li>Improving service quality through usage statistics analysis</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. Personal Information Collected</h2>
      <p>The Company may automatically collect the following information to provide its services:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Device Information</strong>: Device model, operating system version, app version</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Statistics</strong>: App launch count, screen views, feature usage frequency (Firebase Analytics)</li>
        <li><strong>Error Information</strong>: App crash logs, error timestamps and status information (Firebase Crashlytics)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>The Company does not collect personally identifiable information such as names, email addresses, or phone numbers.</p>

      <h2>3. Retention Period</h2>
      <p>Collected information is retained during the service operation period and is promptly destroyed once the purpose of collection is achieved.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Usage statistics data: Automatically deleted after a maximum of 14 months from the date of collection</li>
        <li>Error logs: Automatically deleted after a maximum of 90 days from the date of collection</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Disclosure to Third Parties</h2>
      <p>
        The Company does not, in principle, provide users' personal information to third parties.
        However, exceptions are made in the following cases:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>When the user has given prior consent</li>
        <li>When required by law or requested by investigative agencies in accordance with legally prescribed procedures</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Outsourcing of Personal Information Processing</h2>
      <p>The Company outsources personal information processing for service operation as follows:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Google LLC (Firebase)</strong>: App usage analytics and error collection (<a href="https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Firebase Privacy Policy</a>)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>6. User Rights</h2>
      <p>Users may exercise the following rights at any time:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>You can opt out of analytics data collection in your device settings.</li>
        <li>Deleting the app will immediately stop data collection from that device.</li>
        <li>You can request deletion of collected data.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>7. Privacy Officer</h2>
      <p>For inquiries regarding personal information processing, please contact us at:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Company</strong>: Hyewon & Insong</li>
        <li><strong>Email</strong>: contact@hyewoninsong.com</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        This Privacy Policy is effective from the date stated above. If there are additions, deletions,
        or corrections due to changes in relevant laws or policies, we will notify users through this page
        at least 7 days before the changes take effect.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
